.modal-header
    %button.close{ type:"button", 'data-dismiss' => "modal"}
        %i.icon-remove

    .alert.alert-block
        %h4 
            %i.icon-warning-sign.icon-large
            Attention   
        Les chambres devraient être généré via la commande rake populate:rooms. Modifiez ce script si l'architecture de la rez change.

    %h3 Création d'une chambre

    = bootstrap_flash


= simple_form_for @room do |f|

    .modal-body
        = render partial: "form", locals: {f: f}  

    .modal-footer
        = f.submit "Créer", {class: "btn btn-primary"}